# Hands on

Phil Hands and Luke Leighton have done some [Koolu optimised packages.](http://ftp.hands.com/hands-deb/pool/koolu/)

## Hard drive installation

If you want to give is a try, boot any standard Debian Etch install media, and at
the boot prompt, type:

    auto url=hands.com classes=koolu acpi=off

It's not Webconverger, though it's quite close! From here you should add the Webconverger `/etc/apt/sources.list` line:

    deb http://webconverger.com/debian/ stable/

And be able to install [[extensions|kiosk]] like iceweasel-webconverger. Good luck.
